name: Serenity Caldwell
description: 23-year old wearer of many hats. Macworld staff editor, scribbler, girl wonder.
text:
Guy on bus: "Serenity Caldwell?"
Ren: "Uh... yes?"
GoB: "You should check out my app." [He hands over a postcard.]

So that just happened.

description: My existence, while grotesque and incomprehensible to you, makes people laugh.
